@Kravitz76 1st shot:arm soreness, headache
2nd shot: achy, chills, fever fatigue for 1 day-next morning like nothing happened. 

Interesting side note, almost all of my colleagues were sick after 2, and NONE of our 80 yr old clients had any problems. 😁

@Kravitz76 My Moderna side effects : 
#1.   nothing 
#2.  One sleepless night

@Kravitz76 First shot— super sleepy the next day
Second shot- 12 hours or so of general ickiness starting about 18 hours after the shot

Water, Gatorade, Tylenol will take care of it :)
